历史频道的《{{Internal link helper/en|一号机库：不明飞行物档案|Hangar 1: The UFO Files}}》(2014-2015年播出的电视剧)的《坠毁与掩盖》一集中详细讲述了这一事件。<ref>{{Citation|title="Hangar 1: The UFO Files" Crashes and Cover Ups (TV Episode 2014) - IMDb|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt3641002/plotsummary|access-date=2020-11-09|archive-date=2021-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210811200947/https://www.imdb.com/title/tt3641002/plotsummary|dead-url=no}}</ref>

